Compile
=======
Note that we need to link against an external LAPACK implementation:

  *--[SHELL]----------------------------------------------------------------*
  |                                                                         |
  |  cd flens/examples                                                      |
  |  g++ -std=c++11 -Wall -I../.. -DUSE_CXXLAPACK -framework vecLib      +++|
  |      -o lapack-pbsv lapack-pbsv.cc                                      |
  |                                                                         |
  *-------------------------------------------------------------------------*


Run
===

  *--[SHELL]----------------------------------------------------------------*
  |                                                                         |
  |  cd flens/examples                                                      |
  |  ./lapack-pbsv                                                          |
  |                                                                         |
  *-------------------------------------------------------------------------*

